{"tid":2418423,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想知我星期一Pass咗路試，星期四五攞到牌嘅機會大唔大?","createTime":"2021-02-22T15:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T05:26:22.000Z","uid":257779,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ef00c72e95bb91d829633d3084af1df45d7ac826","tid":2418423,"uid":257779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"小弟唔係幾清楚武漢肺炎下佢啲安排，有冇過來人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（利申：已Google但見佢要排嘅都係關於正式執照）"},{"pid":"170150a7a399d1b56e0a989b2d92b8a7b90834d3","tid":2418423,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"c4813d7854bc7229949533444d3b0f6df6567d96","tid":2418423,"uid":77224,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef00c72e95bb91d829633d3084af1df45d7ac826","tid":2418423,"uid":257779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"小弟唔係幾清楚武漢肺炎下佢啲安排，有冇過來人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（利申：已Google但見佢要排嘅都係關於正式執照）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"份野寫住7個工作日，你等下好不好<br />\n<br />\n今日我先去完金鐘，人龍極長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_press_releases/press_releases/transport_department/index_id_3511.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications_and_press_releases%2Fpress_releases%2Ftransport_department%2Findex_id_3511.html&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=dd48bd2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_press_releases/press_releases/transport_department/index_id_3511.html</a><br />\n<blockquote>由二月十八日起，全面恢復牌照及車輛檢驗服務。<br />\n<br />\n牌照及相關服務<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n運輸署轄下各牌照事務處、公共車輛分組、車輛記錄辦事處、駕駛執照記錄辦事處、違例駕駛記分辦事處及過境服務分組將由二月十八日起全面恢復即時申請的櫃位服務，處理各種牌照及相關服務的申請。<br />\n<br />\n同時，運輸署呼籲市民繼續盡量使用網上預約服務，或利用設置於各牌照事務處的投遞箱、郵寄或經網上遞交申請，以減少在牌照事務處內人群聚集及等候時間。網上預約續領正式駕駛執照／車輛牌照、車輛過戶、保留、轉移或改配車輛登記號碼或申領國際駕駛許可證的每日名額約為五千個，可供網上預約的期間為十星期。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f5e0b0e04f27493f4f6ddf35fd5ed9b8dedb8bf2","tid":2418423,"uid":139187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"用重考生check"},{"pid":"2c464d9ffc3b4dd36737766b437c337605fe839b","tid":2418423,"uid":41352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e0b0e04f27493f4f6ddf35fd5ed9b8dedb8bf2","tid":2418423,"uid":139187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"用重考生check"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"三月十五先開返排期服務，所以呢招做唔到住"},{"pid":"041202d932a1e73b114864b269042af5a73cf86f","tid":2418423,"uid":116696,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"咁心急做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c35952abf2018dd6a3921a4d7f070bf184f8948","tid":2418423,"uid":1767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"拎到機會大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但遲拎早拎咪又係咁"},{"pid":"b6883a3655c576068f8b2cd559421456bcb18045","tid":2418423,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"聽話等一星期，我試過摸門釘"},{"pid":"d2ba1d2c450fb9d47856bcac0ea6eac98bd6a701","tid":2418423,"uid":126961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:24:28.000Z","msg":"考完要7個工作天之後先去得運輸署整 就算之前入箱都要"},{"pid":"24a55d318f65f6f99bcfe4d694c8e541cdd28973","tid":2418423,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T18:17:39.000Z","msg":"唔係有車揸心急做乜"},{"pid":"17800c96be3b8450b343aa8edd6d12f662ce3306","tid":2418423,"uid":322648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"22b82c5c9c14aec5d750f187856b86e64edc2a6b","tid":2418423,"uid":1656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T